  <HediffDef>
    <defName>ST_GainerFrog</defName>
    <label>Clumsy False Toad</label>
    <description>Pumpkin false toads will occasionally injure themselves in the process of performing the backwards somersault phase of a gainer. In competitive diving competitions, a gainer is a form of dive in which the diver performs a full backwards somersault before entering the water in a vertical position.</description>
  	<defaultLabelColor>(255,117,24)</defaultLabelColor>
